                    <p>Whether to turn on the camera flash:<ul>
                    <li><codeph><ph keyref="true"/></codeph>: Turn on the flash.</li>
                    <li><codeph><ph keyref="false"/></codeph>: (Default) Turn off the flash.</li>
                    </ul></p>
                </pd>
            </plentry>
            </parml> </section>
